detail.name: Goku Black
detail.effect: [When Attacking] If you have 7 or fewer cards in your hand, choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards with a cost of 2 or less and place it at the bottom of its owner's deck.

detail.name: ゴクウブラック
detail.effect: 【アタック時】自分の手札が7枚以下の場合、相手のコスト2以下のバトルカード1枚までを選び、デッキの下に置く。
